blog.name: irishpalatines
blog.title: if you got a diamond for your passion
blog.description:
Nic ; Niall is my life, my voice, my reason to be. Here for my five 1D boys as a band and as solo artists. OT5 ride or die. Justin is my babe. 
On this blog: I blog about Louis and Harry being a couple / Liam and Zayn being a couple / OT5 One Direction / I love, enjoy and celebate Niam, Narry, Ziall, Nouis, Zouis, Lilo, Zarry, Lirry as bromances / Zolo, Lolo, Loulo, Holo & Nolo / And I believe that no one loves OT5 more than OT5 themselves.

summary: Just saw a post but i don't want it to my blog but I am saying saying something bc I feel attacked. Yes I am an OT5 stan but...
body: Just saw a post but i don’t want it to my blog but I am saying saying something bc I feel attacked. Yes I am an OT5 stan but that was not the point of the tweet. The tweet was about Liam telling people to stop asking him about 1D. His own solo album is not even out yet and he just wants to do what Zayn, Harry and Niall got to do to. He wants to share his own solo material and maybe do a tour as well. And hell he deserves this so much. Out of the five of them he has been fighting the longest for this. (I am not saying the others didn’t do anything to archieve their dream of course they did but Liam got as far as the judges houses once and then was send home) And now it’s his time. It’s fucking Lolo time and the “OT4” stans only care about him when he puts the words one direction in his mouth and if he does he is getting attacked for it for using it to promote. Yeah he only said ‘other 3’ but that was so not the point of his tweet. He didn’t fucking kill OT5 stans bc that was not what the tweet was about. The tweet was about him and that he hates getting blamed for shit he has no control over. I am OT5 af. Liam includes Zayn most of the time when talking about One Direction. That is only once out of a couple times he didn’t. And it happened on twitter which is a big part of pushing official narrative. I have a beautiful tag called liam is ot5 af if anyone has any doubts there are a few times where Liam showed support to his four boys. (There are some reaches as well pls don’t judge me) But fans who 'only’ saw the 'other 3’ part missed the whole point of the tweet. It doesn’t fucking matter how many members in 1D are. Liam is done with dealing some ot4 fans who don’t respect him as a solo artist. Liam deserves to shine on his own. Louis does too. And Zayn too.
